headline: Schwab Joins Fidelity in Restricting Advisors’ Use of Fintech Tools to Gain Access to Clients’ 401(k)s
summary: Advisors like being able to manage their clients’ retirement-plan assets held at their employers’ administrators, but plan administrators say those services pose a security risk.
